Worst experience ever!!

 I agree shade match doesn’t define the product quality but trust when I applied it on my face the texture seems so off 🥹 it was not blending at all!!
Thick & and full of oil 😳

Don’t trust everything that goes viral ✌🏻

Just sharing my 💕 moments!
 
How fast 2024 is running! We are already near last quarter 🫶

After my maternity leave I thought will get back to my work and my life ( IG Page) but it’s so hard to manage 🥹
I seriously don’t know other Mommies are doing it but I can’t 🥲 the moment I think to start the shoot something or other comes up and I couldn’t complete it!

I thought the newborn phase was hard but no dude Toddler phase is more harder than you imagine 🙃 They will not leave you for a second not even for washroom 🥲

Life is only revolving around my baby 👶 

Anyways it’s just a matter of time 🤞
